Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.65,0:00:50.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Fate doom and future　dark over light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:53.24,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru (get out get out get out get out)
