Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:58.16,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru (get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:00.54,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:05.92,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,錆びついた　shadow prison　姿潜めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:10.47,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,行き場を探しては　I keep my soul in you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.47,0:01:13.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:15.26,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Never give up that fight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.26,0:01:17.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.81,0:01:20.48,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Don't let it claim your light rise
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.48,0:01:25.32,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,果てなきを彷徨う　飽く無き声が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.32,0:01:30.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,足枷を解いて　羽ばたくの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.20,0:01:32.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,時間の狭間で召されてく魂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.99,0:01:35.45,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,たとえ全てを焼き尽くされたとし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:40.12,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,ても　飲み込んで　しまえば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:45.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,闇を振り翳して　胸に宿すアンサー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:47.63,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1370,27)}闇中反転　照らして
