Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:50.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FF&\3c&H0000FF&\3a&HFF&\pos(1370.666,35)}Won't you make yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:50.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1720,74.668)} -> 探すの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.01,0:01:52.22,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,君を守りたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:54.84,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,そのに呼びかけるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:59.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,闇中宣戦　全身全霊　生きてゆく証
